Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Asiimov
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.
Covert Skins.lore: Anyone can predict the future... a visionary shapes it

Covert Skins.name: AWP | Neo-Noir
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with two stylized blue-magenta women over a grayscale background.
Covert Skins.lore: "They took comfort in each other's despair"

Classified Skins.name: UMP-45 | Momentum
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with bright colors and forward facing arrows.

Classified Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Mecha Industries
Classified Skins.desc: Its white and black design feels both sterile and futuristic.
Classified Skins.lore: Same technology, now available in a smaller form factor

Classified Skins.name: MP5-SD | Phosphor
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted by dripping neon pink, green, and teal paint onto its dark base.

Restricted Skins.name: USP-S | Flashback
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted in an attempt to make a suggestion about the duality of man.

Restricted Skins.name: Galil AR | Signal
Restricted Skins.desc: A hydrographic pattern of red hexagons has been applied over a dark blue base.

Restricted Skins.name: MAC-10 | Pipe Down
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to appear as if it is filled with red tubes.

Restricted Skins.name: P250 | Nevermore
Restricted Skins.desc: A bright orange pattern of skeletal birds has been applied.
Restricted Skins.lore: Claim your spot in the pecking order

Restricted Skins.name: G3SG1 | Scavenger
Restricted Skins.desc: Originally green, parts of the weapon have been replaced with street signs and a tomato can.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SG 553 | Danger Close
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with a metallic-fire themed design.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Glock-18 | Oxide Blaze
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A custom paint job has been applied with a rust-colored base and white detailing.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: "The subject claims this washed up on shore"

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Nova | Wood Fired
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Its woodgrain base has been painted green and finished with blue accents and burned-in flames.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: M4A4 | Magnesium
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with flames and a winged defuser in white atop a dark grey base.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Black Sand
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a tan and black military camo pattern.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Mikah did not account for highly motivated opposition

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Tec-9 | Fubar
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The muzzle of this military themed weapon has been scorched with use.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: You call it used, we call it well-loved

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP9 | Modest Threat
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with an orange and black design.
